title: Data-Driven Exploration of National Health Service Talking Therapies Care Pathways Using Process Mining: Retrospective Cohort Study
details: E Yardley, A Davis, C Eldridge, C Vasilakis - JMIR Mental Health, 2024
abstract: Background: The National Health Service (NHS) Talking Therapies program treats people with common mental health problems in England according to “stepped care,” in which lower-intensity interventions are offered in the first instance, where …
